  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a registry of human hepatocytes (liver cells) for research purposes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients scheduled for partial hepatectomy/liver surgery are asked permission to use their
      discarded liver tissue for purposes of studying:

        1. how drugs/medicines affect the liver and

        2. the effects of storing liver cells in the cold or freezing.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
